  +opentyrian-20090423.ebuild:
  New snapshot, upstream has improved the loudness (music) code. Delete old
  ebuild.

  15 Apr 2009; Torsten Veller <tove@gentoo.org> opentyrian-20090222.ebuild:
  Add ~x86 (#266229)

